<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Analytics — Trust Layer</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/dashboard-layout.css">
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,700;1,400;1,500&family=Outfit:wght@200;300;400;500&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    *,
    *::before,
    *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      background: var(--cream);
      color: var(--ink);
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── UNDER CONSTRUCTION UX ── */
    .construction-container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 120px);
      padding: 40px 20px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .construction-card {
      background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, #1B242C, #13191e);
      border-radius: 2em;
      padding: 50px 40px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 480px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .construction-card::before {
      content: '';
      background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--honey), var(--amber));
      position: absolute;
      top: -3px;
      left: -3px;
      right: -3px;
      bottom: -3px;
      z-index: -2;
      border-radius: 2.1em;
    }

    .icon-glow {
      position: relative;
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .gear-large {
      position: absolute;
      animation: rotate-clockwise 8s linear infinite;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .gear-small {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50px;
      right: 10px;
      animation: rotate-counter 6s linear infinite;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    @keyframes rotate-clockwise {
      from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
      to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
    }

    @keyframes rotate-counter {
      from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
      to { transform: rotate(-360deg); }
    }

    .construction-card h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #ffffff;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .construction-card p {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(243, 235, 217, 0.7);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .progress-bar-wrap {
      width: 100%;
      height: 6px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .progress-bar {
      width: 70%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--honey), var(--amber));
      border-radius: 10px;
      animation: progress-pulse 2s infinite ease-in-out;
    }

    @keyframes progress-pulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.85; }
      50% { opacity: 1; }
    }

    .status-text {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: var(--honey);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .back-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 100%;
      height: 46px;
      background: transparent;
      border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      border-radius: 50px;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.25s ease;
    }

    .back-btn:hover {
      border-color: var(--honey);
      color: var(--honey);
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(250, 87, 22, 0.15);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <%- include('partials/sidebar', { active: 'analytics' }) %>

  <!-- MAIN -->
  <div class="main">
    <%- include('partials/topbar', { pageTitle: 'Analytics', pageSub: 'Scan intelligence dashboard' }) %>
    
    <div class="content" style="overflow-y: auto; overflow-x: hidden;">
      
      <!-- UNDER CONSTRUCTION CONTAINER -->
      <div class="construction-container">
         <div class="construction-card">
            <div class="icon-glow">
               <!-- Animated gears -->
               <svg class="gear-large" viewBox="0 0 64 64" width="80" height="80">
                  <path fill="var(--honey)" d="M54.1 36.3c.1-.8.2-1.6.2-2.3 0-.7-.1-1.5-.2-2.3l6.5-5.1c.6-.5.7-1.3.4-1.9l-6.2-10.7c-.4-.6-1.1-.9-1.8-.6l-7.7 3.1c-1.6-1.2-3.4-2.2-5.3-3l-1.2-8.2c-.1-.7-.7-1.2-1.4-1.2h-12.4c-.7 0-1.3.5-1.4 1.2l-1.2 8.2c-1.9.8-3.7 1.8-5.3 3l-7.7-3.1c-.7-.3-1.4 0-1.8.6L6.4 24.7c-.4.6-.3 1.4.4 1.9l6.5 5.1c-.1.8-.2 1.6-.2 2.3 0 .7.1 1.5.2 2.3l-6.5 5.1c-.6.5-.7 1.3-.4 1.9l6.2 10.7c.4.6 1.1.9 1.8.6l7.7-3.1c1.6 1.2 3.4 2.2 5.3 3l1.2 8.2c.1.7.7 1.2 1.4 1.2h12.4c.7 0 1.3-.5 1.4-1.2l1.2-8.2c1.9-.8 3.7-1.8 5.3-3l7.7 3.1c.7.3 1.4 0 1.8-.6l6.2-10.7c.4-.6.3-1.4-.4-1.9l-6.5-5.1zm-22.1 6.5c-4.9 0-8.8-3.9-8.8-8.8s3.9-8.8 8.8-8.8 8.8 3.9 8.8 8.8-3.9 8.8-8.8 8.8z"/>
               </svg>
               <svg class="gear-small" viewBox="0 0 64 64" width="48" height="48">
                  <path fill="var(--amber)" d="M54.1 36.3c.1-.8.2-1.6.2-2.3 0-.7-.1-1.5-.2-2.3l6.5-5.1c.6-.5.7-1.3.4-1.9l-6.2-10.7c-.4-.6-1.1-.9-1.8-.6l-7.7 3.1c-1.6-1.2-3.4-2.2-5.3-3l-1.2-8.2c-.1-.7-.7-1.2-1.4-1.2h-12.4c-.7 0-1.3.5-1.4 1.2l-1.2 8.2c-1.9.8-3.7 1.8-5.3 3l-7.7-3.1c-.7-.3-1.4 0-1.8.6L6.4 24.7c-.4.6-.3 1.4.4 1.9l6.5 5.1c-.1.8-.2 1.6-.2 2.3 0 .7.1 1.5.2 2.3l-6.5 5.1c-.6.5-.7 1.3-.4 1.9l6.2 10.7c.4.6 1.1.9 1.8.6l7.7-3.1c1.6 1.2 3.4 2.2 5.3 3l1.2 8.2c.1.7.7 1.2 1.4 1.2h12.4c.7 0 1.3-.5 1.4-1.2l1.2-8.2c1.9-.8 3.7-1.8 5.3-3l7.7 3.1c.7.3 1.4 0 1.8-.6l6.2-10.7c.4-.6.3-1.4-.4-1.9l-6.5-5.1zm-22.1 6.5c-4.9 0-8.8-3.9-8.8-8.8s3.9-8.8 8.8-8.8 8.8 3.9 8.8 8.8-3.9 8.8-8.8 8.8z"/>
               </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>Under Construction</h2>
            <p>Our Advanced Scan Analytics dashboard is currently being engineered for <%= brandname %>. Soon you'll be able to track live scans, geo-locations, and counterfeit signals in real-time.</p>
            
            <div class="progress-bar-wrap">
               <div class="progress-bar"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="status-text">SYSTEM DEVELOPMENT IN PROGRESS — 70%</div>

            <a href="/dashboard" class="back-btn">
               <span>Return to Dashboard</span>
            </a>
         </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>